                                    <p>June kicks off a busy time of year with graduations, Father&rsquo;s Day, end of the school year, 4th of July, vacations &amp; of course the Jersey Shore! We are thrilled to bring you the summer <b>Showcase Magazine</b> to plan for all your special events. Discover the many wonderful<b> LOCAL</b> merchants and use <b>The Showcase</b> <b>Magazine</b> as your &ldquo;Summer Guide&rdquo; to all things <b>LOCAL!</b> In addition, our featured articles, brought to you by our talented writers, offer ideas for your summer and vacations. </p>
                                    <p>This year&rsquo;s June cover, &ldquo;Helping Hands&rdquo; is brought to you by Laura Lee Zanghetti a Boston native. Ms. Zanghetti is known for her beach scenes which makes her painting perfect for our cover. </p>
                                    <p>We would like to welcome our new advertisers as well as returning ones and encourage you to support these <b>LOCAL</b> businesses and your community. </p>
                                    <p>We have <b>Showcased </b>6 advertisers with <b>Showcase Salutes;</b> please take the time to read all about these <b>LOCAL</b> businesses and their success stories. Featured salutes include: <b>Blue Fountain Day Spa, Bonji</b> <b>Bowls, Country Squire, Dean&rsquo;s Greens Garden, Nursery &amp; Floral Center, La Bella Vita Wellness &amp; Relaxation Center &amp; Mark Schottenfeld of Berkshire Hathaway.</b></p>
                                    <p>On page 40, you can enjoy the <b>Summer Word Find</b> and have a chance at winning 6 tickets to a Somerset Patriots game of your choice. No better way to enjoy your family than at a <b>LOCAL</b> baseball game! Just solve it, fax it in and it&rsquo;s that easy to win! </p>
                                    <p>In the spirit of Giving Back<b>, </b><b>The Showcase Magazine</b> continues to donate to the community. To view a list of organizations that we have supported, visit our website at <a href="http://www.theshowcasemagazine.net" target="_blank"><b>www.theshowcasemagazine.net</b></a> and click on the Giving Back Tab. The <b>Giving Back</b> Column <b>Showcases </b>3 organizations looking for donations and time and The <b>Community Chatter</b> is always full of wonderful events, local businesses and organizations donating in many ways. </p>
                                    <p><b>The Showcase</b> is available ON-LINE at <a href="http://www.theshowcasemagazine.net" target="_blank"><b>www.theshowcasemagazine.net</b></a>. Follow us on Twitter &amp; Instagram <b><a href="https://twitter.com/@('@')theshowcasemag" target="_blank">@@TheShowcaseMag</a></b> and friend us on Facebook at <b><a href="http://www.facebook.com/TheShowcaseMagazine" target="_blank">www.facebook.com/TheShowcaseMagazine</a></b>. This allows our advertisers to increase their visibility and helps to promote their goods. </p>
                                    <p>Our <b>ON-LINE Business Guide</b> is bigger and better than ever with over 100 businesses and new additions joining every day! Just go to <a href="http://www.theshowcasemagazine.net" target="_blank"><b>www.theshowcasemagazine.net</b></a> and click on Business Guide. You will find categories to make it easy to navigate and find exactly what you are looking for. Can&rsquo;t find it? Just email or call us and we will be more than happy to refer you to the business you are looking for. </p>
                                    <p>As always, we would like to thank our readers and advertisers for supporting us and the <b>LOCAL</b> businesses and professionals of <b>The Showcase</b> <b>Magazine</b> who make it possible for us to give back to the community for the past 21 years! We urge you to <b>SHOP SMART &amp; SHOP LOCAL </b>&amp; remember <b>LOCAL IS THE BEST PLACE TO BE!</b></p>
                                    <p>Wishing you and your families a safe &amp; relaxing summer! </p>
